總知 中唔到獎 就係有問題<br />\n藍屍聽到都反<br />\n派4000蚊後又一災難"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T16:15:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">個網邊間公司做？<br />\n政府比左幾錢做？<br />\n有無公開招標？</span>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T16:16:49.000Z","msg":"audit應獨立調查佢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T16:35:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2b68dd65884119031c7fed11f267e9911154b71f","tid":1807114,"uid":60297,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T16:37:15.000Z","msg":"唔應該對港共政府心存丁點期望<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ebfcce1c77e4ddbc88d33a66d4edc4a94a6cb6e","tid":1807114,"uid":266362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T16:39:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">［急尋人！］</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1月1日 銅鑼灣citibank前被捕手足去向 <br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1807139\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1807139</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n求幫推"},{"pid":"594947fc45c7f8322a1a3d3587aa8fabd28379d7","tid":1807114,"uid":266362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T16:39:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">［急尋人！］</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1月1日 銅鑼灣citibank前被捕手足去向 <br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1807139\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1807139</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" c